00:52:08,860 --> 00:52:09,930
I didn't get the scholarship.

539
00:52:14,790 --> 00:52:16,780
Aren't you sad then?

540
00:52:17,390 --> 00:52:19,240
Look at me. I'm so sad.

541
00:52:19,240 --> 00:52:19,680
Didn't you see?

542
00:52:25,840 --> 00:52:26,790
P'Kit,

543
00:52:28,400 --> 00:52:31,070
that was so fake.

544
00:52:33,970 --> 00:52:37,370
Who told me to apply
for this stupid scholarship?

545
00:52:37,990 --> 00:52:42,670
Who was the one who said
he wanted to get the scholarship?

546
00:52:43,100 --> 00:52:45,210
I just didn't want to hold you back.

547
00:52:46,960 --> 00:52:47,980
Were you worried?

548
00:52:48,290 --> 00:52:48,650
Do you know

549
00:52:48,650 --> 00:52:50,150
that this is a stupid plan?

550
00:52:52,290 --> 00:52:55,320
Do you know how much this stupid plan
had caused me to miss you?

551
00:52:58,300 --> 00:53:00,280
I missed you even more.

552
00:53:23,080 --> 00:53:26,240
I'm going to become the pirate king!

553
00:53:29,370 --> 00:53:30,630
Hmm.

554
00:53:37,800 --> 00:53:39,320
The TV is so far away now.

555
00:53:44,210 --> 00:53:46,210
Look, this is Charlotte Linlin.

556
00:53:50,070 --> 00:53:52,510
Look, Luffy's eyes are gigantic.

557
00:53:52,510 --> 00:53:53,280
Look at my eyes.

558
00:53:53,280 --> 00:53:54,700
Are my eyes as huge as Luffy's?

559
00:54:31,960 --> 00:54:32,830
P'Kit,

560
00:54:33,390 --> 00:54:39,540
do you wish to do it here?
Or do you wish to do it on the bed?

561
00:54:42,060 --> 00:54:43,290
Aren't you stating the obvious?

562
00:55:32,930 --> 00:55:33,720
Finally,

563
00:55:35,310 --> 00:55:37,980
you long for me as much as I long for you.

564
00:55:51,030 --> 00:55:52,750
Do you love me?

565
00:55:55,260 --> 00:55:56,110
I do.

566
00:55:57,950 --> 00:55:59,220
And I love you very much.

567
00:56:02,770 --> 00:56:04,490
I love you too.

568
00:57:21,950 --> 00:57:23,510
Don't hug the wrong person again.

569
00:57:24,290 --> 00:57:25,920
Who said I hugged the wrong person?

570
00:57:27,000 --> 00:57:31,340
♫ I don't know what made me fall in love ♫

571
00:57:27,350 --> 00:57:29,170
I had hugged the right person
since that day.

572
00:57:30,820 --> 00:57:32,190
Why did you do so?

573
00:57:31,340 --> 00:57:36,090
♫ I don't know why,
but my heart is shaking ♫

574
00:57:33,450 --> 00:57:34,470
What are you thinking?

575
00:57:36,090 --> 00:57:38,380
♫ Even though I saw your silhouette ♫

576
00:57:38,380 --> 00:57:44,910
♫ I couldn't see clearly who was
walking towards me ♫

577
00:57:40,340 --> 00:57:42,140
I'm afraid I have to spend the night here

578
00:57:43,060 --> 00:57:44,910
to avoid the rain.

579
00:57:45,250 --> 00:57:46,900
♫ The only thing I know ♫

580
00:57:46,900 --> 00:57:49,440
♫ Is that I fell for you ♫

581
00:57:49,440 --> 00:57:51,940
♫ Just like that ♫

582
00:57:51,940 --> 00:57:53,860
♫ Because it's you ♫

583
00:57:53,860 --> 00:57:56,070
♫ What do you want to do? ♫

584
00:57:56,070 --> 00:57:58,330
♫ What do you want from me? ♫

585
00:57:58,330 --> 00:58:00,800
♫ Why did I fall for you? ♫

586
00:58:00,800 --> 00:58:05,270
♫ I fell for you without any reason ♫

587
00:58:05,270 --> 00:58:10,230
♫ I'll be satisfied
as long as you're here ♫

588
00:58:10,230 --> 00:58:12,470
♫ I feel happy ♫

589
00:58:12,470 --> 00:58:14,720
♫ When I can see you ♫

590
00:58:14,720 --> 00:58:18,600
♫ And listen to your voice ♫

591
00:58:18,600 --> 00:58:23,040
♫ I miss you without any reason ♫

592
00:58:23,040 --> 00:58:24,780
♫ Whenever I close my eyes ♫

593
00:58:24,780 --> 00:58:28,040
♫ You appear in my heart clearly ♫

594
00:58:28,040 --> 00:58:30,280
♫ I don't know why ♫

595
00:58:30,280 --> 00:58:32,500
♫ And I don't know how to control it ♫

596
00:58:32,500 --> 00:58:34,710
♫ Just let it be ♫

597
00:58:34,710 --> 00:58:39,290
♫ Because I don't need
a reason to fall for you ♫

598
00:58:55,790 --> 00:59:00,290
♫ No one ordered me to love you ♫

599
00:59:00,290 --> 00:59:01,940
♫ I didn't fall for you on purpose ♫

600
00:59:01,940 --> 00:59:04,990
♫ It was an accident ♫

601
00:59:04,990 --> 00:59:07,180
♫ The closer I am to you ♫

602
00:59:07,180 --> 00:59:07,830
♫ The closer I can see your eyes ♫
